Corrine, aren't we?

52
00:06:12,556 --> 00:06:15,787
Hello! Everybody, hello?
Hi.

53
00:06:16,526 --> 00:06:19,154
I'd like to say some stuff
about Corrine.

54
00:06:19,496 --> 00:06:21,657
About a year ago,
she came out for a visit and...

55
00:06:21,865 --> 00:06:24,163
I took her out to my clinic
on the reservation.

56
00:06:24,368 --> 00:06:27,030
And there was this
little girl there, Olivia...

57
00:06:27,304 --> 00:06:29,738
who had terrible stomach cramps.

58
00:06:29,940 --> 00:06:34,103
And she was so shy
that I couldn't, you know...

59
00:06:34,310 --> 00:06:35,902
