And suddenly
I hear this gigantic burp.

62
00:06:43,619 --> 00:06:44,950
Corrine.

63
00:06:45,988 --> 00:06:48,855
And then she burped again.
And then Olivia burped.

64
00:06:49,058 --> 00:06:52,391
And then they were going back
and forth like a couple of sailors!

65
00:06:52,929 --> 00:06:54,658
And problem solved.

66
00:06:55,197 --> 00:06:57,631
If you've got a belly full of gas,
it's gotta go somewhere, right?

67
00:06:57,833 --> 00:07:00,233
I'll never forget it. I mean...

68
00:07:01,470 --> 00:07:03,802
Corrine was so special.

69
00:07:06,241 --> 00:07:07,333
Excuse me.

70
00:07:07,642 --> 00:07:10,304
