71
00:07:10,645 --> 00:07:13,239
-Troy, you remember the Tollivers?
-Certainly.

72
00:07:13,448 --> 00:07:15,780
-We met at the viewing.
-Barbaric ritual.

73
00:07:15,984 --> 00:07:17,076
