aren't ya?

105
00:10:19,461 --> 00:10:21,224
Alright, fine.
Look, there's a cute waitress there.

106
00:10:21,430 --> 00:10:22,920
I can't do it by myself.
You know how I get.

107
00:10:23,131 --> 00:10:25,622
Well, I think you're probably
gonna be okay by yourself.

108
00:10:25,834 --> 00:10:27,699
But I got like a week on this thing
and I don't...

109
00:10:27,903 --> 00:10:29,734
-You're not gonna eat for a week?
-Not what I said.

110
00:10:29,938 --> 00:10:31,997
Didn't say I wasn't gonna eat
for a week. I'm not feeling hungry.

111
00:10:32,207 --> 00:10:35,005
Willy, I said no.
Okay? I said no.

112
00:10:41,283 --> 00:10:42,841
I'm gonna...

113
00:10:44,052 --> 00:10:46,612
-Alright, Mexican. There's a cute...
-Can you give me a break on this one?

114
00:10:46,822 --> 00:10:49,984
I'm not hungry, I got work to do.
I don't...

115
00:10:51,259 --> 00:10:52,385
Alright.

116
00:10:52,593 --> 00:10:55,528
I don't eat Mexican...

117
00:10:57,265 --> 00:10:58,960
food.

118
00:11:09,343 --> 00:11:10,810
Fine.

119
00:12:15,874 --> 00:12:18,001
Hey, honey, I'm home.

120
00:12:18,377 --> 00:12:21,175
I hope you're hungry 'cause
I am in the mood to cook.

121
00:12:21,380 --> 00:12:23,109
And no, you can't help.

122
00:12:23,315 --> 00:12:25,545
I'm gonna make that salmon thing
we had at that restaurant...

123
00:12:25,751 --> 00:12:27,684
near the place where
we almost bought the puppy.

124
00:12:27,885 --> 00:12:29,250
You know, I never told you this,
but I...

125
00:12:29,454 --> 00:12:31,718
almost went back the next day
and bought it anyway.

126
00:12:31,923 --> 00:12:34,448
I know they trash the house
and pee on everything...

127
00:12:34,659 --> 00:12:37,594
but it'd be good practice
for when we decide to have...

128
00:12:40,498 --> 00:12:44,332
Why so glum?

129
00:12:45,203 --> 00:12:49,196
We will have none of that
in my house.

130
00:12:57,215 --> 00:13:01,446
Besides, whatever it is,
it's nothing that can't be fixed...

131
00:13:01,651 --> 00:13:06,850
