148
00:15:34,867 --> 00:15:36,459
<i>Especially now</i>.

149
00:15:37,570 --> 00:15:41,061
<i>Who knows? Maybe you'll even</i>
<i>figure out how to uncross the stars</i>.

150
00:15:41,273 --> 00:15:43,070
<i>I nevercould</i>.

151
00:15:43,642 --> 00:15:47,908
<i>I love you for always and ever</i>.
<i>Corrine."</i>

