Is there a pay phone?

163
00:16:55,712 --> 00:16:58,203
Sure. Out by the jerky.

164
00:16:58,414 --> 00:17:00,405
Thank you.

165
00:17:02,952 --> 00:17:05,512
Oh, my. My, my, my.

166
00:17:37,052 --> 00:17:38,144
