What do you want me to do?

173
00:17:56,237 --> 00:17:58,728
-I don't know!
-Okay, okay, okay.

174
00:17:58,939 --> 00:18:01,772
All right, well,
you just breathe, okay?

175
00:18:01,976 --> 00:18:04,001
Oh, my God.

176
00:18:06,247 --> 00:18:08,340
Oh, my God!
You are really doing this.

177
00:18:08,549 --> 00:18:12,849
You really are doing this.
Okay. Okay.

178
00:18:13,054 --> 00:18:16,956
Look at me.
Breathe. Breathe. Breathe.

179
00:18:17,158 --> 00:18:19,456
That's it.
Okay, give me my hand.

180
00:18:19,660 --> 00:18:21,991
That's it. Oh, my God!

181
00:18:24,030 --> 00:18:26,123
We have a head!

182
00:18:26,332 --> 00:18:28,527
Okay. Okay.
Look at me. Look at me.

183
00:18:28,735 --> 00:18:30,669
Give me a push.
Give me a push.

184
00:18:30,870 --> 00:18:33,566
That's it. Okay.
That's it. One more.

185
00:18:33,773 --> 00:18:34,831
That's it.

186
00:18:36,042 --> 00:18:37,771
Oh, my God!

187
00:18:43,817 --> 00:18:46,411
