188
00:18:50,957 --> 00:18:54,687
Oh, my God.

189
00:18:55,694 --> 00:18:57,161
It's a little girl.

190
00:18:57,362 --> 00:19:00,126
Oh, my God.

191
00:19:00,499 --> 00:19:03,093
Oh, my God.
