221
00:23:26,690 --> 00:23:28,624
Excuse me.

222
00:23:34,465 --> 00:23:37,229
Do you know where the pool is?

223
00:23:37,434 --> 00:23:39,959
I'm not deaf, son.
I just wasn't paying any attention.

224
00:23:40,204 --> 00:23:41,262
I'm sorry, man, I...

225
00:23:41,472 --> 00:23:45,168
Better to keep your mouth shut
and look stupid...

226
00:23:45,441 --> 00:23:48,968
than open it and remove all doubt.

227
00:23:49,245 --> 00:23:52,612
Okay. I'm supposed to meet
my aunt at the pool.

228
00:23:53,149 --> 00:23:54,616
Who's your aunt?

229
00:23:54,951 --> 00:23:58,216
Hilda Limberlost.

230
00:24:03,259 --> 00:24:06,285
Robert. Walden.
Call me Bobby.

231
00:24:06,562 --> 00:24:08,154
-I'm Troy Harper.
-The nephew.

232
00:24:08,364 --> 00:24:10,559
Yeah. I came out here
to build my aunt a porch.

233
00:24:10,767 --> 00:24:12,860
Corrine come with you?

234
00:24:13,770 --> 00:24:16,135
I met her the last time
she was out here.

235
00:24:16,338 --> 00:24:18,465
Sharp girl. I always wanted
to meet the guy she picked.

236
00:24:18,673 --> 00:24:20,038
