237
00:24:26,181 --> 00:24:29,207
I'm truly sorry to hear that.

238
00:24:29,718 --> 00:24:31,413
Yeah, me too.

239
00:24:32,120 --> 00:24:36,079
I'm sorry.
Where did you say the pool was?

240
